SUMMARY:It Goes On
DESCRIPTION:$3 wine & poetry \nReadings by Samar Abulhassan\, Kevin Emerson\, Ramon Isao\, and Arlene Naganawa \nThursday\, March 26\, 7pm \nDoors at 6pm \nHugo House is delighted to partner with poet Jeanine Walker and mixed media artist Aaron Counts to bring It Goes On to the Hugo House stage! It Goes On features $3 glasses of wine\, $12 bottles\, and invaluable words. March 26 stars poets Samar Abulhassan and Arelene Naganawa\, and fiction writers Kevin Emerson and Ramon Isao. Come on out to our cozy cabaret-style theater to partake in the words\, wine\, and full-on spring fun.
URL:https://hugohouse.org/event/_2026-03-26/
CATEGORIES:Mainstage,Community Event
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR